data.description: $5,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS/RATE BUY-DOWN // Make your best offer and be #HomefortheHolidays!     Looking for space in all the right places? With over 2,800 SqFt, this grand home sitting on just over a 1/4 acre (on a corner), offers super-sized bedrooms with an XL loft! The spacious primary bedroom with high ceilings, bay window, and adjoining bath are on the first floor. There's room for everything and everyone!        PLANNING TO HOST FOR THE HOLIDAYS? Greet your guests from the foyer and welcome them into your decorated formal dining area. Carve your turkey, serve dessert, and recline in the living room to watch the game!    CALL YOUR FAVORITE AGENT and tour the home today!
